{"tid":1080869,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[五毛服務零售版] 僅需付$50，五分鐘內可被誇讚過百次！","createTime":"2019-03-28T01:46:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T00:10:29.000Z","uid":1886,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"318e465db669c67d2743b1e0f80e332acb9d308a","tid":1080869,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T01:46:26.000Z","msg":"【支那新潮語：彩虹屁？】<br />\n【俾錢「誇誇群」稱讚服務　讚到你天上有地下無】<br />\n<br />\n繼「低級紅、高級黑」，支那再現一個新潮語「彩虹屁」。在淘寶搜尋一下，過百個搜尋結果都聲稱提供「稱讚服務」，讚你、讚你的朋友、伴侶、家人和上司都可以。有些更標榜是由知名大學的學生為你度身訂造，誓要「誇到你懷疑人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」。這些服務由一元一分鐘，到一百元一小時都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n究竟花錢是不是買到開心？我們的記者給50元試過。群主首先會私信問背景，包括「服務對象是誰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」和「為甚麼要人讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」，之後將買家加到一個80人的群組。你不必說話，他們已經「眾星拱月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」，而且有求必應。吟詩作對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，或笑話一則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，都為搏你一笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n五分鐘之內被人稱讚過百次，如此落力稱讚一個陌生人，除了為賺幾元，對他們來說還有甚麼意義？「誇誇群」群友阿龔指：「買家進來群的時候，假如因為一些小事，自己可能放不開，感覺比較難過。不知道看到這些讚美的詞，他是怎麼樣的反應。」<br />\n<br />\n「如果有人跟他互動，最好的效果是可以幫助這個人，減輕他當前的心理壓力。」<br />\n<br />\n讀大學一年級的阿龔說，這種服務是今年「婦女節」之後興起，本身只有「無厘頭」的稱讚。後來演變成度身訂造，哄人開心的服務，參與的大多是大學生。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/374257519970872\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F374257519970872&d=5mmA4sQKuQaI7%2FjJJ4WTl0YzBSotcsoJ75UENuGtOl4%3D&h=baf3e34b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/374257519970872</a><br />\n（有線中國組，有片）"},{"pid":"c4df382b535d0a1ddd964aacc459cf9fb6214870","tid":1080869,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T01:47:08.000Z","msg":"騎呢服務不只一樣，「代喝」服務同樣有市場。在百度貼吧上，有網民以「卡路里是他的」、「快樂是你的」做招徠，聲稱收20元幫你喝飲料。讓你不用親自出馬，都有食評和配相放上社交媒體，讓人羨慕羨慕。<br />\n<br />\n隨著單身經濟的盛行，有評論認為這些以低成本獲取暫時精神滿足的消費，在未來可能愈來愈普及。"},{"pid":"686d638179276206d57d092cdca6ac2afdcec0fd","tid":1080869,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T01:58:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">網民回應</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fkyF6sv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfkyF6sv.png&h=f4e4e015&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DdTnAkR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDdTnAkR.png&h=3bee2ff5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2605c600acfaf504bfe501d27b2cc43004712c21","tid":1080869,"uid":100347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T02:07:29.000Z","msg":"這些服務由一元一分鐘，到一百元一小時都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n買59個一分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f21cd1c9b698e7df3e0e767e52b6b00530df539","tid":1080869,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T02:59:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: purple;\"></span>"},{"pid":"ae9d2ea9b4e84120328c6361a5a6583655ad36d1","tid":1080869,"uid":161945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2605c600acfaf504bfe501d27b2cc43004712c21","tid":1080869,"uid":100347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T02:07:29.000Z","msg":"這些服務由一元一分鐘，到一百元一小時都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n買59個一分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T03:01:44.000Z","msg":"再轉售一小時服務俾人收番1